1/0


LS5(1:OFF 
                        0:ON C+)




PB4


1/0


LS4(1:OFF 
                        0:ON C-)




PB3


1/0


LS3(1:OFF 
                        0:ON B+)




PB2


1/0


LS2(1:OFF 
                        0:ON B-)




PB1


1/0


LS1(1:OFF 
                        0:ON A+)




PB0


1/0


LS0(1:OFF 
                        0:ON A-)



輸入控制範例
IF 
                  INP(433)=170 /* 1010 1010*/



完成狀態


說明




A氣缸


A-




